    {
      "id": "04bb8261-e944-424a-8573-e3cd44438c54",
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "Example 2 (variables, types, assignment, and expressions): Write the equivalent Java code for the Python program below\n\n    score = 5\n    a = 1\n    b = 2\n    print(a // b == 0)\n    print(a/b == 0.5)",
