      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "Example 3 (statements): Write the equivalent Java code for the Python program below\n\n    dryMass = 100\n    propellantMass = 56\n    vehicleMass = dryMass + \\\n                  propellantMass\n    print(vehicleMass)  ",
