      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "Example 7 (arrays): Write the equivalent Java code for the Python program below\n\n    u = [3, 1, 4]\n    v = 3*u[0]\n    for i in range(len(u)):\n        v[i] = 2*u[i]\n    print(v)",
